      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura movimento su file                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       scr-mov-fil-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se inserimento non si esaminano le righe dele-  *
      *              * tate                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    =    "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-200.
       scr-mov-fil-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura riga "last removed"                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "LR"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se fine : a trattamento righe "in vita"         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to scr-mov-fil-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se riga precedente non esistente : riciclo      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
           if        w-rig-num-prg (2)    =    zero
                     go to scr-mov-fil-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Delete [zvf]                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-rec-zvf-000      thru del-rec-zvf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Riciclo a prossima "last removed"               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-100.
       scr-mov-fil-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Determinazione del flag di variazioni in testa- *
      *              * ta che si ripercuotono anche sulle righe        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-var-tes-cor      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Start su righe corpo                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se start non valida : uscita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to scr-mov-fil-700.
       scr-mov-fil-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura sequenziale righe corpo                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se at end : uscita                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to scr-mov-fil-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattamento file righe [zvf]                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se inserimento                              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-mfu-tip-fun    not  = "I"
                     go to scr-mov-fil-500.
       scr-mov-fil-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Write record [zvf]                      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   wrt-rec-zvf-000      thru wrt-rec-zvf-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se modifica                                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga nuova : come inserimento        *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-num-prg (2)    =    zero
                     go to scr-mov-fil-400.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Controllo se riga corpo variata o se    *
      *                      * variazioni in testata che si riper-     *
      *                      * cuotono sulle righe                     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-val-aep (1)    not  = w-rig-val-aep (2) or
                     w-cnt-var-tes-cor    not  = spaces
                     go to scr-mov-fil-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga corpo non variata               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo suc-   *
      *                          * cessiva                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-600.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se riga corpo variata                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Rewrite [zvf]                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   rew-rec-zvf-000      thru rew-rec-zvf-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo suc-   *
      *                          * cessiva                             *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           go to     scr-mov-fil-300.
       scr-mov-fil-700.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Nessun trattamento file testata                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       scr-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Delete movimento da file                                  *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-mov-fil-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione righe                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Start su righe corpo                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ST"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           move      1                    to   w-cat-rig-num          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se start non valida : a testata             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to del-mov-fil-500.
       del-mov-fil-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Lettura sequenziale righe corpo             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   w-cat-rig-ope          .
           perform   cll-sub-cat-000      thru cll-sub-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se at end : a testata                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cat-rig-exs        not  = spaces
                     go to del-mov-fil-500.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Movimento da buffer catena movimenti a work *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-cat-rig-buf        to   w-rig                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delete record file righe [zvf]              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-rec-zvf-000      thru del-rec-zvf-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo a lettura riga corpo successiva     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     del-mov-fil-100.
       del-mov-fil-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Cancellazione testata file [zvf]                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Delete record [zvf]                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   del-rec-zvf-000      thru del-rec-zvf-999        .
       del-mov-fil-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Composizione record righe [zvf]                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cmp-rec-zvf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione record                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "NO"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzvf"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zvf                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-num-def (1)    to   rf-zvf-num-def         .
           move      w-rig-cod-def (1)    to   rf-zvf-cod-def         .
           move      w-tes-cod-lng        to   rf-zvf-cod-lng         .
           move      w-rig-des-stp (1)    to   rf-zvf-des-stp         .
           move      w-rig-alx-exp (1)    to   rf-zvf-alx-exp         .
       cmp-rec-zvf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Scrittura record righe [zvf]                              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       wrt-rec-zvf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-zvf-000      thru cmp-rec-zvf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Put record                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PT"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzvf"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zvf                 .
       wrt-rec-zvf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Riscrittura record righe [zvf]                            *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       rew-rec-zvf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione record                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   cmp-rec-zvf-000      thru cmp-rec-zvf-999        .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Force Put record                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "FP"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzvf"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zvf                 .
       rew-rec-zvf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Cancellazione record righe [zvf]                          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       del-rec-zvf-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione chiave primaria                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-rig-num-def (2)    to   rf-zvf-num-def         .
           move      w-rig-cod-def (2)    to   rf-zvf-cod-def         .
           move      w-tes-cod-lng        to   rf-zvf-cod-lng         .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Delete record                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DE"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzvf"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zvf                 .
       del-rec-zvf-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Box per messaggio di errore                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       box-msg-err-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Salvataggio immagine video                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "SV"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in Off                                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Box                                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      12                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      13                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      14                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      68                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Messaggio nel box                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      48                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      15                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-err-box-err-msg    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Parentesi quadre di delimitazione               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      03                   to   v-car                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      64                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      "[ ]"                to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Video in On                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Accettazione carattere di presa visione         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "AC"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "K"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      13                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      65                   to   v-pos                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ripristino immagine video                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       box-msg-err-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Routine di lettura archivio [zln]                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       let-arc-zln-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione marker di uscita                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zln-flg      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test se codice lingua a spazi                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-zln-cod    =    spaces
                     go to let-arc-zln-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura per codice                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODLNG"             to   f-key                  .
           move      w-let-arc-zln-cod    to   rf-zln-cod-lng         .
           move      "pgm/dcc/fls/ioc/obj/iofzln"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zln                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to let-arc-zln-400.
       let-arc-zln-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bufferizzazione valori                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-zln-des-lng       to   w-let-arc-zln-des      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     let-arc-zln-999.
       let-arc-zln-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Azioni per record non trovato                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-zln-flg      .
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-zln-des      .
           go to     let-arc-zln-999.
       let-arc-zln-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zln-des      .
       let-arc-zln-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per allineamenti a destra o a sinistra oppure *
      *    * al centro di campi alfanumerici di varia lunghezza, fi-   *
      *    * no ad un massimo di 240 caratteri, oppure per il conca-   *
      *    * tenamento, con o senza separazione, di max 10 substrin-   *
      *    * ghe in una unica substringa                               *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "swd/std/prg/cpy/wallstr0.cps"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per l'accettazione del codice lingua          *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "pgm/dcc/prg/cpy/acodzln0.acs"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Subroutines per l'accettazione valore descrizione aggiun- *
      *    * tiva in fattura                                           *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
           copy      "pgm/dcc/prg/cpy/acodzvf0.acs"                   .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Richiamo sottoprogramma per gestione catena righe         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cll-sub-cat-000.
           call      "pgm/dcc/prg/obj/pdcc0902"
                                         using w-cat-rig              .
       cll-sub-cat-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Cancellazione sottoprogramma per gestione catena righe    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cnc-sub-cat-000.
           cancel    "pgm/dcc/prg/obj/pdcc0902"                       .
       cnc-sub-cat-999.
           exit.

